Umwi akati kabo wakali kubona masimpe kuti Daniel nkwali ciindi nobalikondelezya abeenzinyina naa ciindi nobaunka kuyakuuma bbola . ”
Mazuba aano , Daniel alimwi abanyina bapona buyo kabotu .
Kwaamba masimpe , kuli nzila zinji nzyotukonzya kubelesya kuumbulizya baabo balila .
Ibbaibbele alyalo lilatuumbulizya kwiinda mukutupa bulangizi bwakumbele bukkomanisya .
Ibamwi balalemba madeeti aabantu bakafwa amakkalenda aabo kutegwa kaabayeezya ciindi nobeelede kuumbulizya baabo bakafwidwa .
Mulakonzya kuyeeya kuti ba Gail , ibaambwa kumatalikilo aazibalo eezyi , baladooneka naa kuli nobayooluluba lufwu lwabalumi babo , ba Rob .
Nokuba boobo , balangila kuyoobabona alimwi munyika mpya njasyomezyede Leza .
Ndilabafwida luzyalo bantu ibakafwidwa bayandwa babo pele ibatajisi bulangizi bwakuyoobabona alimwi . ”
Lino - lino , eeci Leza ncayoocitila Jobu alimwi abantu bambi batabaliki — ciindi nyika eeyi yaakusandulwa kuba paradaiso .
Eeci Bbaibbele lilacisinizya mulugwalo lwa Milimo 24 : 15 noliti : “ Kuyooba bubuke . ”
Jesu utusyomezya kuti : “ Mutagambwi amakani aaya , nkaambo ciyoosika ciindi eelyo aabo boonse ibali muzyuumbwe nobayoomvwa ijwi lyakwe akuzwa mulinzizyo . ”
Unoojisi bulangizi bwakuba ‘ anguzu zyabukubusi ’ alimwi , mubili wakwe ‘ unooli muteteete kwiinda wamwana ’ mane kukabe kutamani .
Eeci nceciyoocitika kuli baabo boonse ibatondezya kulumba kucipego ca Leza cabubuke anyika .
Ikuti naa mwakafwidwa muyandwa wanu , twaambo ootu ntotwabandika ambweni tatukonzyi kubumanina limwi buumba boonse mbomujisi .
Pele kwiinda mukuzinzibala kuyeeya zisyomezyo zya Leza izijanika mu Bbaibbele , mulakonzya kuba abulangizi bwini - bwini alimwi akuyumizyigwa . — 1 Batesalonika 4 : 13 .
Sena inga mwayanda kwiiya zinji kujatikizya mbomukonzya kuliyumya ciindi nomuli mubuumba ?
Naa sena kuli mibuzyo iimbi njomujisi iiswaangene amakani aaya , mbuli wakuti , “ Nkaambo nzi Leza ncalekelede bubi akupenga ? ”
Twamulomba kuti mulange awebbusaiti yesu ya jw.org / toi , kutegwa mulibonene Bbaibbele mbolipa bwiinguzi buumbulizya alimwi bugwasya kapati .
“ Leza . . . uyoosindula misozi yoonse kumeso aabo , alimwi lufwu talukabi limbi . ” — Ciyubunuzyo 21 : 3 , 4 .
Magazini eeyi ya Ngazi Yamulindizi ilapandulula Leza mbwayoocizuzikizya cisyomezyo eeci alimwi ancocikonzya kwaamba kulindinywe .
MAKANI AAYEEME AMUTWE UULI ACIVWUMBYO | NKAAMBO NZI JESU NCAAKAPENGELA AKUFWA ?
Mumwaka wa 33 C.E . , Jesu waku Nazareta wakajaigwa .
Wakatamikizyigwa kubukila cisi , wakaumwa citaambiki , akugagailwa acisamu cakupenzyezya .
Pele Leza wakamubusya , mpoonya nokwakainda mazuba aali 40 , Jesu wakaunka kujulu .
Eeci cibalo cilibedelede tucijana mumabbuku one aa Makani Mabotu aazwa mu Magwalo aa Banakristo aa Chigiriki , kanji - kanji aitwa kuti Cizuminano Cipya .
Kulubazu lumwi , ikuti naa zintu eezyi zyakacitika ncobeni , nkokuti kuli bulangizi bubotu kubantu , bwalo oobo mbomukonzya kulangila .
Aboobo , sena zibalo izili mu Makani Mabotu nzyamasimpe naa nzyakuyeeyela buyo ?
Mukwiimpana atwaano twakaindi twakuyeeyela buyo , Makani Mabotu akalembwa munzila iiluzi alimwi iisyomeka .
Mucikozyanyo , alijisi mazina aamasena manji aaliko ncobeni , bunji bwangawo alakonzya kuswaigwa mazuba aano .
Alatwaambila kujatikizya bantu ibakapona ncobeni alimwi ibakasinizyigwa abasikulemba makani aakaindi . — Luka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Jesu ulaambwa abasikulemba makani bamumwaanda wamyaka wakusaanguna awabili .
* Mbolupanduludwe lufwu lwakwe kweelana a Makani Mabotu , kuleendelana anzila bana Roma nzyobakali kubelesya kujaya bantu kuciindi eeco .
Kuyungizya waawo , zintu izyakacitika zyakalembwa munzila iitondezya kuti zyamasimpe alimwi zilasyomeka , mane buya akuyubununa bulubizi bwabasikwiiya ba Jesu bamwi .
Twaambo ootu toonse tutondezya kuti balembi ba Makani Mabotu bakali kusyomeka alimwi bakaliluzi kumakani ngobakalemba kujatikizya Jesu .
Nokuba kuti Jesu ulizyibidwe kapati kuti wakapona akufwa , bamwi balabudooneka bubuke bwakwe .
Nobaba baapostolo bakwe kumatalikilo tiibakaasyoma makani aakuti wabuka .
Nokuba boobo , kudooneka koonse kwakamana ciindi balo alimwi abasikwiiya bambi nobakamubona ziindi ziindene - indene Jesu iwakabusyigwa .
Mubwini , aciindi cimwi , bantu bainda ku 500 bakamubona ntongolameso . — 1 Bakorinto 15 : 6 .
Kwiinda mukulibikka muntenda yakwaangwa akujaigwa , basikwiiya bakakambauka cabusicamba kujatikizya bubuke bwa Jesu kubantu boonse — nokuba kuli baabo ibakamujaya .
Sena basikwiiya banji boobu nobakaba basicamba ikuti nobatakali masimpe kuti Jesu wakabusyigwa ncobeni ?
Mubwini , bubuke bwa Jesu mbombubo bwakali kukulwaizya Bunakristo kaindi alimwi amazuba aano .
Makani Mabotu aamba zyalufwu alimwi abubuke bwa Jesu alazizumina zintu zyoonse ziyandika zyamasimpe , izyakalembwa kaindi .
Kuzibala cakusitikila kuyakumugwasya kusyoma kuti zintu eezyi zyakacitika ncobeni .
Lusyomo lwanu lulakonzya kuyuma ciindi nomumvwisya kaambo ncozyakacitikila .
Tacitus , iwakazyalwa kuma 55 C.E . , wakalemba kuti “ Kristo , ooko ikwakazwa zina lyakuti [ Banakristo ] , wakapenga kapati mubweendelezi bwa Tiberiyo kuli Ponto Pilato imuleli wesu . ”
Jesu alimwi ulaambwa a Suetonius ( mumwaanda wamyaka wakusaanguna ) ; sikulemba zyakaindi mu Juda uutegwa Josephus ( mumwaanda wamyaka wakusaanguna ) ; alimwi a Pliny mweendelezi waku Bithynia ( kumatalikilo aamwaanda wamyaka wabili ) .
Kuyungizya waawo , takulangilwi kuti bunji bwabasikukazya Jesu bakali kukonzya kulemba cili coonse kugwasya bantu kuti bamusyome Jesu .
Kujatikizya bubuke bwa Jesu , Petro , umwi wabaapostolo bakwe wakapandulula kuti : “ Leza wakamubusya ooyu muntu mubuzuba bwatatu akumupa kuti alibonye , ikutali kubantu boonse pe , pele kuli bakamboni bakasalilwa limwi a Leza , kulindiswe , nitwakalya akunywa anguwe naakabuka kuzwa kubafwu . ”
Makani Mabotu aa Matayo atwaambila kuti basololi bazikombelo nobakamvwa kuti Jesu wabusyigwa , bakasola kujana nzila yakulesya makani aaya kuti atamwaiki . — Matayo 28 : 11 - 15 .
Sena eeci caamba kuti Jesu wakalikuyanda kuti bubuke bwakwe butazyibwi ?
Peepe , nkaambo Petro wakaamba kuti : “ Wakatulailila kukambaukila bantu akupa bumboni cakulomya bwakuti muntu ooyu ngonguwe wakasalwa a Leza kuti abe mubetesi wabaumi abafwide . ”
Banakristo bakasimpe balacita oobo . — Milimo 10 : 42 .
“ Mbubonya cibi mbocakanjila munyika kwiinda mumuntu omwe [ Adamu ] alufwu kwiinda mucibi . ” — Baroma 5 : 12
Ino inga mwaingula buti kuti mwabuzyigwa kuti , “ Sena mulayanda kupona kukabe kutamani ? ”
Bantu banji balakonzya kwaamba kuti balayanda pele balimvwa kuti tacigwasyi kubandika makani aaya .
Baamba kuti , lufwu nkoluli talutijigwi .
Pele mbuti kuti mubuzyo nguwenya wacincwa mpoonya mwabuzyigwa kuti , “ Sena mulilibambilide kufwa ? ”
Cakutadooneka , bantu banji inga baingula kuti peepe .
Bbaibbele litondezya kuti Leza wakabalenga bantu kabajisi luyandisisyo lwakupona .
Mubwini lyaamba kuti , “ wabikka abuumi butamani mumyoyo yabo . ” — Mukambausi 3 : 11 .
Nokuba boobo , bwini mbwakuti , bantu tabakonzyi kupona kukabe kutamani .
Kuyungizya waawo , sena Leza kuli ncacitide kululamika zintu ?
Bwiinguzi bwamu Bbaibbele bulakulwaizya alimwi buliswaangene akaambo Jesu ncaakapengela akufwa .
Zyaandaano zyakusaanguna zyotatwe zyabbuku lyamu Bbaibbele lya Matalikilo zitwaambila kuti Leza wakabapa bulangizi bwabuumi butamani banabukwetene bakusaanguna ba Adamu a Eva , alimwi wakabaambila ncobakeelede kucita kutegwa babujane buumi oobo .
Kumane cibalo cilaamba mbobakaalilwa kumvwida Leza alimwi akusweekelwa bulangizi oobu .
Cibalo tacikatazyi kumvwa cakuti bamwi bayeeya kuti ncaano buyo .
Mbuli mabbuku aa Makani Mabotu , alyalo bbuku lya Matalikilo lilatondezya mbocili camasimpe cibalo caamba makani aakaindi .
Ncinzi cicitikide akaambo kakutamvwida kwa Adamu ?
Bbaibbele liingula boobu : “ Mbubonya cibi mbocakanjila munyika kwiinda mumuntu omwe alufwu kwiinda mucibi , eelyo lufwu lwakasikila bantu boonse nkaambo boonse bakabisya . ”
Aboobo wakasweekelwa coolwe cabuumi butamani mpoonya wakafwa .
Mbotuli bana bakwe , twakakona cibi cakwe .
Pele sena Leza kuli ncacitide kutegwa zintu zilulame ?
Leza wakapanga bubambe bwakunununa , naa kujola ceeco Adamu ncaakasweekelwa alunyungu lwakwe , nkokuti bulangizi bwabuumi butamani .
Kulugwalo lwa Baroma 6 : 23 Bbaibbele lyaamba kuti : “ Cakuvwola cacibi ndufwu . ”
Eeci caamba kuti lufwu lwakaboola akaambo kacibi .
Mbubwenya buyo tulabisya , aboobo ncotujana ncakuvwola cacibi , nkokuti lufwu .
Pele twakazyalwa mucibi nokuba kuti swebo lwesu tiitwakabisya .
Aboobo , caluyando Leza wakatuma Mwanaakwe Jesu , kutegwa atununune kuzwa ‘ kucakuvwola cazibi ’ zyesu .
Lufwu lwa Jesu lujalula nzila iisololela kubuumi butamani , bukkomanisya
Mbwaanga muntu omwe , uulondokede Adamu , wakaleta cibi alufwu kulindiswe akaambo kakutamvwida , muntu uulondokede uumvwida kusikila kulufwu wakali kuyandika kutegwa atwaangunune kucibi alufwu .
Bbaibbele lipandulula boobu : “ Mbubonya ibanji mbobakaba basizibi kwiinda mukutamvwida kwamuntu omwe , mbubonya buyo kwiinda mukumvwida kwamuntu omwe ibanji bayooba balulami . ”
Wakazwa kujulu , wakaba muntu uulondokede * , akufwa akaambo kandiswe .
Akaambo kaceeci , cilakonzyeka kulindiswe kumvwana a Leza akuba acoolwe cakupona kukabe kutamani .
Nkaambo nzi ncocakali kuyandika kuti Jesu afwe kutegwa azuzikizye makanze aaya ?
Sena Leza Singuzuzyoonse tanaakali kukonzya buyo kwaambila balunyungu lwa Adamu kuti bazumizyigwa kupona kukabe kutamani ?
Ikuti Leza naatakacita bululami , bantu nobakatalika kuzumbauzya kuti naa wakali kukonzya kucita oobo amutwaambo tumbi .
Mucikozyanyo , sena naatakasalulula caboola kukusala iwakali kweelela kupona kukabe kutamani akati kabana ba Adamu ?
Sena wakali kukonzya kusyomwa caboola kukuzuzikizya zisyomezyo zyakwe ?
Kukakatila kwa Leza kubululami kutegwa tujane lufwutuko , ncisinizyo cakuti lyoonse unoocita ziluleme .
Kwiinda mucipaizyo calufwu lwa Jesu , Leza wakajalula coolwe cabuumi butamani mu Paradaiso anyika .
Amubone majwi aa Jesu aalembedwe mulugwalo lwa Johane 3 : 16 aakuti : “ Leza wakaiyanda kapati nyika cakuti wakapa Mwanaakwe simuzyalwaalikke , kutegwa muntu uuli woonse uumusyoma atanyonyoonwi , pele abe abuumi butamani . ”
Aboobo , lufwu lwa Jesu ncitondezyo cabululami bwa Leza , ikapati luyando lwakwe lupati kubantu .
Nokuba boobo , nkaambo nzi Jesu ncaakali kuyandika kupenga akufwa munzila iicisa yalo yaambidwe mumabbuku aa Makani Mabotu ?
Kwiinda mukulibombya mumusunko muyumu kapati alimwi akuzumanana kusyomeka , Jesu wakakazya cakumaninina kutamikizya kwa Diabolosi kwakuti bantu tabakonzyi kuzumanana kusyomeka kuli Leza ikuti basunkwa .
Kutamikizya ooku nikwakaboneka kuti nkwamasimpe ciindi Saatani naakayunga Adamu wakalondokede kuti abisye .
Pele Jesu ooyo iwakeelene a Adamu kulondoka , wakazumanana kusyomeka nomuba mumapenzi manji .
Aboobo wakatondezya kuti awalo Adamu naakamumvwida Leza ikuti naakasala kucita oobo .
Kwiinda mukuliyumya mumasunko , Jesu wakatusiila citondezyo cibotu cakuti katutobela .
Leza wakamupa bulumbu Mwanaakwe akaambo kakumvwida cakumaninina , wakapa Jesu buumi butafwi kujulu .
Jesu wakatondezya ncotweelede kucita naakati : “ Eeci caamba buumi butamani , ikuti bakuzyiba yebo O Leza mwini - mwini ooli olikke , ayooyo ngookatuma , Jesu Kristo . ” — Johane 17 : 3 .
Balembi bamagazini eeyi bamutamba kuti mwiiye zinji kujatikizya Jehova , Leza wakasimpe , alimwi akujatikizya Mwanaakwe , Jesu Kristo .
Bakamboni ba Jehova ibali mucilawo canu bayookkomana kumugwasya .
