SENA INGA MWAAMBA KUTI Diabolosi . . .
Mbube buyo bubyaabi ibuli mumuntu ?
Diabolosi wakaambaula alimwi ‘ akumusunka ’ Jesu .
Kuzwa kumatalikilo , Diabolosi wakali mungelo uusalala , pele “ kunyina naakakakatila mukasimpe . ”
Wakaba mubeji alimwi wakazangila Leza .
Abamwi bangelo bakamutobela . — Ciyubunuzyo 12 : 9 .
Diabolosi woofwaazya bantu banji kutegwa batamuzyibi . — 2 Bakorinto 4 : 4 .
BANTU BAMWI BAAMBA KUTI bweendelezi bwa Diabolosi mbubi , kakuli bamwi balayoowa kunjilwa myuuya mibi .
“ Nyika yoonse ili mumaanza aamubi . ”
Diabolosi ulabayunga kapati bantu , pele teendelezyi bantu boonse pe .
Diabolosi ubelesya kubeja kutegwa ayunge bantu . — 2 Bakorinto 11 : 14 .
Zimwi ziindi myuuya mibi ilakonzya kweendelezya bantu . — Matayo 12 : 22 .
